<br>
He/She will try and dot you first thing so it's working on you the whole time...this being the case, you want to kill him asap.<br>
<br>
Stick to lures as your basic nukes...you don't have time for resists and stuff...<br>
<br>
Their heal snares them if i remember correctly...drop a rain on them, will force them to try and move, preventing any casting as well.<br>
<br>
Use shock of lightning (our lvl 12 knockback spell) ...i've seen a wiz just constantly cast that and own other classes lol...  Shaman spells will take a while to cast, watch for it and use it accordingly.  If they back into a wall/corner and you can't push them back with this spell, use Rain...that'll make them move unless they are dumb.<br>
<br>
Bust out the damn sword pet....they never see this coming and throws them into shock as they get confused and casting interrupted, throw all your nukes fast.<br>
<br>
Get some damn cure potions, if he gets those dots on you, even if you win...your'e gonna die soon after...i forget which but i believe the poison dots arn't dispellable.<br>
<br>
